# Engine features

- [x] ascii set/unset

``` yaml
ascii_composer
  switch_key:
    Shift_L: noop
    Shift_R: noop
    Alt_L: set_ascii_mode
    Alt_R: unset_ascii_mode
    Super_L: set_ascii_mode
    Super_R: unset_ascii_mode
```

- [x] commit digit seperator

``` yaml
punctuator:
  digit_separator_action: commit # or false
```

- [x] punctuator: digit seperator

``` yaml
punctuator:
  digit_separators: ",.;'"
```

- [x] auto complete longer word

``` yaml
translator:
  enable_completion: true
```

- [?] When predicting

Key binding condition: {when: predicting}

- failed 

